4"></span>临</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y7a ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">死之前一心念佛，<span class="_ _4"></span>结果癌症奇迹般地消失了。<span class="_ _6"></span>所以，<span class="_ _4"></span>有时候</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yd6 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">心的力量非常神奇。 </div><div class="t m0 x23 h4 y11f ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">其实，<span class="_ _4"></span>我们每个人都会死亡，<span class="_ _6"></span>只不过是迟早而已。<span class="_ _4"></span>假如</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y59 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">死到临头才开始信佛，临时抱佛脚，这不一定能扭转乾坤。</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5a ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">所以，<span class="_ _4"></span>希望大家也能以此为戒，<span class="_ _6"></span>对死亡提前要有所准备。<span class="_ _4"></span>古</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5b ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">往今来，<span class="_ _5"></span>不少佛教徒在死时特别安详，<span class="_ _4"></span>这是什么原因呢？就</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
